  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_0' aria-label=\" Manjunath Tirakappa Malagi and Anr. versus Gurusiddappa Tirakappa Malagi (Dead through Lrs) pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('0','2025','2025_4_1409_1416','2025INSC514'); ><font size='4'> <strong>MANJUNATH TIRAKAPPA MALAGI AND ANR.<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>GURUSIDDAPPA TIRAKAPPA MALAGI (DEAD THROUGH LRS) </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 4 S.C.R. 1409</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 514</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010005152025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : SUDHANSHU DHULIA<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, AHSANUDDIN AMANULLAH</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Whether a fresh suit can be filed to challenge a compromise decree. Headnotes&dagger; Code of Civil Procedure, 1908 &ndash; Suit seeking partition claiming that the suit property is not ancestral property &ndash; Held, the suit property purchased by funds in the name of the father of the appellant is joint family property &ndash; The appellants contended that since the suit property is not an ancestral property, it cannot be partitioned amongst their father, grandfather and father&rsquo;s brothers &ndash; The Appellants further<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 21-04-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CIVIL APPEAL No. 5373/2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Dismissed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('0','2025','2025_4_1409_1416','2025INSC514','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('0','2025','2025_4_1409_1416','2025INSC514','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('0','2025','2025_4_1409_1416','2025INSC514');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('0','2025','2025_4_1409_1416','2025INSC514','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
